Package: bmmix
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Mixed Models Using the Extended Beta of the Third Kind
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hilde", "Vinje", email = "hilde.vinje@nmbu.no", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Lars Erik", "Gangsei", email = "lars.gangsei@nmbu.no", role = "aut"))
Description: Implements a closed-form Bayesian posterior for simple, 
  balanced mixed-effect linear regression models using the Extended Beta 
  Distribution of the Third Kind. The package includes tools for posterior 
  evaluation and supports empirical Bayes strategies for setting hyperparameters.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
